The FY15                 acquisition plan currently anticipates production of 18,500 (or more) US Topo maps                 this year. Interested parties who wish to become a data acquisition partner with the                 USGS in FY15 or in future years should contact a USGS Geospatial Liaison -                 http://liaisons.usgs.gov/geospatial/documents/TNM_Partnership_User_ContactList.pdf.</abstract>             <purpose> </purpose>             <supplinf/>         </descript>         <timeperd>
